-- BHP Billiton to Sell Mount Nimba Project, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-07-15T10:17:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/bhp-billiton-to-sell-mount-nimba-project-sunday-times-says.html
BHP Billiton Ltd. (BHP)  is selling its
Guinea, West Africa-based Mount Nimba iron-ore project, the
 Sunday Times  reported, without saying where it obtained the
information.  BHP hired  Nomura Holdings Inc. (8604)  to find a buyer, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
 echarlton1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
